data.description: Welcome to this sophisticated 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo in the desirable Greenhouse Residences of Cherry Creek! Immerse yourself in the expansive open-concept living space, with an abundance of natural light,  and contemporary flooring throughout. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, ample counters, and a seamless bar top that flows effortlessly into the spacious living room. Adjacent to the living area is a versatile flex space, perfect for an office or tailored to your preferences. Step out onto the balcony from here to enjoy city views! The generously appointed primary bedroom features a walk-in closet and an attached bathroom. Enjoy practical conveniences like an in-unit laundry room with a washer/dryer and a designated parking spot in a secure garage. Enjoy an array of building amenities, including wifi, a fitness center, communal kitchen, garden, bike storage, and a business center. Ideally located in Cherry Creek, with close proximity to premier shopping, dining, trails, parks, and easy access to I-25, downtown Denver, and the mountains. Don't miss the chance to secure this exceptional home! Buyers receive a $2,000 credit for a rate buy-down or closing costs when utilizing our preferred lender. Elevate your lifestyle in this extraordinary residence!
